{"data":[{"name":"56:1","price":"When the Inevitable Event comes to pass,","arabic":"إِذَا وَقَعَتِ ٱلۡوَاقِعَةُ","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":4980,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"en"},{"name":"56:2","price":"there will be none to deny its occurrence;","arabic":"لَيۡسَ لِوَقۡعَتِهَا كَاذِبَةٌ","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":4981,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"en"},{"name":"56:3","price":"it will bring some low and raise others up[1].","arabic":"خَافِضَةٞ رَّافِعَةٌ","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":4982,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"[1] According to their deeds rather than wealth and social position, as is the case in this world. The righteous will be elevated in Paradise and the wicked will be debased in Hell.","lang":"en"},{"name":"56:4","price":"When the earth is shaken violently,","arabic":"إِذَا رُجَّتِ ٱلۡأَرۡضُ رَجّٗا","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":4983,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"en"},{"name":"56:5","price":"and the mountains crushed to pieces,","arabic":"وَبُسَّتِ ٱلۡجِبَالُ بَسّٗا","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":4984,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"en"},{"name":"56:6","price":"and turn to scattered dust,","arabic":"فَكَانَتۡ هَبَآءٗ مُّنۢبَثّٗا","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":4985,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"en"},{"name":"56:7","price":"then you are sorted into three groups:","arabic":"وَكُنتُمۡ أَزۡوَٰجٗا ثَلَٰثَةٗ","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":4986,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"en"},{"name":"56:8","price":"the people of the right – how blessed will be the people of the right[2]!","arabic":"فَأَصۡحَٰبُ ٱلۡمَيۡمَنَةِ مَآ أَصۡحَٰبُ ٱلۡمَيۡمَنَةِ","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":4987,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"[2] i.e., those who receive their record of deeds in the right hand and are destined for Paradise.","lang":"en"},{"name":"56:9","price":"The people of the left – how miserable will be the people of the left[3]!","arabic":"وَأَصۡحَٰبُ ٱلۡمَشۡـَٔمَةِ مَآ أَصۡحَٰبُ ٱلۡمَشۡـَٔمَةِ","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":4988,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"[3] i.e., those who receive their record of deeds in the left hand and are destined for Hell.","lang":"en"},{"name":"56:10","price":"And the forerunners [in faith] are the forerunners [in Paradise].","arabic":"وَٱلسَّٰبِقُونَ ٱلسَّٰبِقُونَ","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":4989,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"en"},{"name":"56:11","price":"They are the nearest ones [to Allah],","arabic":"أُوْلَٰٓئِكَ ٱلۡمُقَرَّبُونَ","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":4990,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"en"},{"name":"56:12","price":"in Gardens of Bliss,","arabic":"فِي جَنَّٰتِ ٱلنَّعِيمِ","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":4991,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"en"},{"name":"56:13","price":"many from the early generations,","arabic":"ثُلَّةٞ مِّنَ ٱلۡأَوَّلِينَ","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":4992,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"en"},{"name":"56:14","price":"and a few from the later generations.","arabic":"وَقَلِيلٞ مِّنَ ٱلۡأٓخِرِينَ","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":4993,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"en"},{"name":"56:15","price":"[They will be seated] on jeweled couches,","arabic":"عَلَىٰ سُرُرٖ مَّوۡضُونَةٖ","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":4994,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"en"},{"name":"56:16","price":"reclining on them, facing one another.","arabic":"مُّتَّكِـِٔينَ عَلَيۡهَا مُتَقَٰبِلِينَ","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":4995,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"en"},{"name":"56:17","price":"They will be served by immortal youths","arabic":"يَطُوفُ عَلَيۡهِمۡ وِلۡدَٰنٞ مُّخَلَّدُونَ","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":4996,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"en"},{"name":"56:18","price":"with cups, pitchers, and glasses [of wine] from a flowing spring,","arabic":"بِأَكۡوَابٖ وَأَبَارِيقَ وَكَأۡسٖ مِّن مَّعِينٖ","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":4997,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"en"},{"name":"56:19","price":"which will neither cause any headache nor intoxication,","arabic":"لَّا يُصَدَّعُونَ عَنۡهَا وَلَا يُنزِفُونَ","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":4998,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"en"},{"name":"56:20","price":"along with fruits of their choice,","arabic":"وَفَٰكِهَةٖ مِّمَّا يَتَخَيَّرُونَ","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":4999,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"en"},{"name":"56:21","price":"and flesh of birds that they may desire.","arabic":"وَلَحۡمِ طَيۡرٖ مِّمَّا يَشۡتَهُونَ","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":5000,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"en"},{"name":"56:22","price":"And [they will have] maidens with wide gorgeous eyes,","arabic":"وَحُورٌ عِينٞ","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":5001,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"en"},{"name":"56:23","price":"like pristine pearls,","arabic":"كَأَمۡثَٰلِ ٱللُّؤۡلُوِٕ ٱلۡمَكۡنُونِ","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":5002,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"en"},{"name":"56:24","price":"as a reward for what they used to do.","arabic":"جَزَآءَۢ بِمَا كَانُواْ يَعۡمَلُونَ","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":5003,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"en"},{"name":"56:25","price":"They will not hear therein any idle talk or sinful speech,","arabic":"لَا يَسۡمَعُونَ فِيهَا لَغۡوٗا وَلَا تَأۡثِيمًا","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":5004,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"en"},{"name":"56:26","price":"except the words of peace, peace[4].","arabic":"إِلَّا قِيلٗا سَلَٰمٗا سَلَٰمٗا","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":5005,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"[4] i.e., only exchanging greetings of peace.","lang":"en"},{"name":"56:27","price":"The people of the right – how blessed will be the people of the right!","arabic":"وَأَصۡحَٰبُ ٱلۡيَمِينِ مَآ أَصۡحَٰبُ ٱلۡيَمِينِ","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":5006,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"en"},{"name":"56:28","price":"[They will be] in the midst of thornless lote trees,","arabic":"فِي سِدۡرٖ مَّخۡضُودٖ","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":5007,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"en"},{"name":"56:29","price":"and clusters of bananas,","arabic":"وَطَلۡحٖ مَّنضُودٖ","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":5008,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"en"},{"name":"56:30","price":"and extended shade,","arabic":"وَظِلّٖ مَّمۡدُودٖ","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":5009,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"en"},{"name":"56:31","price":"and flowing water,","arabic":"وَمَآءٖ مَّسۡكُوبٖ","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":5010,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"en"},{"name":"56:32","price":"and abundant fruit –","arabic":"وَفَٰكِهَةٖ كَثِيرَةٖ","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":5011,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"en"},{"name":"56:33","price":"neither ceasing nor restricted –","arabic":"لَّا مَقۡطُوعَةٖ وَلَا مَمۡنُوعَةٖ","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":5012,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"en"},{"name":"56:34","price":"and elevated mattresses [on beds].","arabic":"وَفُرُشٖ مَّرۡفُوعَةٍ","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":5013,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"en"},{"name":"56:35","price":"Indeed, We have perfectly created them [i.e., their spouses],","arabic":"إِنَّآ أَنشَأۡنَٰهُنَّ إِنشَآءٗ","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":5014,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"en"},{"name":"56:36","price":"and have made them virgins,","arabic":"فَجَعَلۡنَٰهُنَّ أَبۡكَارًا","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":5015,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"en"},{"name":"56:37","price":"loving and of equal age,","arabic":"عُرُبًا أَتۡرَابٗا","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":5016,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"en"},{"name":"56:38","price":"for the people of the right,","arabic":"لِّأَصۡحَٰبِ ٱلۡيَمِينِ","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":5017,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"en"},{"name":"56:39","price":"many from the earlier generations,","arabic":"ثُلَّةٞ مِّنَ ٱلۡأَوَّلِينَ","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":5018,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"en"},{"name":"56:40","price":"and many from the later generations.","arabic":"وَثُلَّةٞ مِّنَ ٱلۡأٓخِرِينَ","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":5019,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"en"},{"name":"56:41","price":"And the people of the left – how wretched will be the people of the left!","arabic":"وَأَصۡحَٰبُ ٱلشِّمَالِ مَآ أَصۡحَٰبُ ٱلشِّمَالِ","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":5020,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"en"},{"name":"56:42","price":"[They will be] in scorching wind and scalding water,","arabic":"فِي سَمُومٖ وَحَمِيمٖ","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":5021,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"en"},{"name":"56:43","price":"in the shade of black smoke,","arabic":"وَظِلّٖ مِّن يَحۡمُومٖ","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":5022,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"en"},{"name":"56:44","price":"neither cool nor refreshing.","arabic":"لَّا بَارِدٖ وَلَا كَرِيمٍ","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":5023,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"en"},{"name":"56:45","price":"Indeed, they used to be in luxuries before,","arabic":"إِنَّهُمۡ كَانُواْ قَبۡلَ ذَٰلِكَ مُتۡرَفِينَ","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":5024,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"en"},{"name":"56:46","price":"and persisted in the gravest sin[5].","arabic":"وَكَانُواْ يُصِرُّونَ عَلَى ٱلۡحِنثِ ٱلۡعَظِيمِ","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":5025,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"[5] i.e., Shirk (associating partners with Allah) or disbelief.","lang":"en"},{"name":"56:47","price":"They used to say, \"When we die and become dust and bones, will we really be raised again?","arabic":"وَكَانُواْ يَقُولُونَ أَئِذَا مِتۡنَا وَكُنَّا تُرَابٗا وَعِظَٰمًا أَءِنَّا لَمَبۡعُوثُونَ","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":5026,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"en"},{"name":"56:48","price":"And our forefathers as well?”","arabic":"أَوَءَابَآؤُنَا ٱلۡأَوَّلُونَ","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":5027,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"en"},{"name":"56:49","price":"Say, [O Prophet], “Indeed, the former and later generations","arabic":"قُلۡ إِنَّ ٱلۡأَوَّلِينَ وَٱلۡأٓخِرِينَ","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":5028,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"en"},{"name":"56:50","price":"will be gathered on a predetermined Day.","arabic":"لَمَجۡمُوعُونَ إِلَىٰ مِيقَٰتِ يَوۡمٖ مَّعۡلُومٖ","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":5029,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"en"},{"name":"56:51","price":"Then you, O misguided deniers,","arabic":"ثُمَّ إِنَّكُمۡ أَيُّهَا ٱلضَّآلُّونَ ٱلۡمُكَذِّبُونَ","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":5030,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"en"},{"name":"56:52","price":"will surely eat from the tree of zaqqūm[6],","arabic":"لَأٓكِلُونَ مِن شَجَرٖ مِّن زَقُّومٖ","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":5031,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"[6] See footnote 44:43-46.","lang":"en"},{"name":"56:53","price":"filling your bellies with it,","arabic":"فَمَالِـُٔونَ مِنۡهَا ٱلۡبُطُونَ","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":5032,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"en"},{"name":"56:54","price":"and drinking scalding water on top of it,","arabic":"فَشَٰرِبُونَ عَلَيۡهِ مِنَ ٱلۡحَمِيمِ","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":5033,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"en"},{"name":"56:55","price":"drinking like thirsty camels do.”","arabic":"فَشَٰرِبُونَ شُرۡبَ ٱلۡهِيمِ","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":5034,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"en"},{"name":"56:56","price":"This will be their welcome on the Day of Judgment.","arabic":"هَٰذَا نُزُلُهُمۡ يَوۡمَ ٱلدِّينِ","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":5035,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"en"},{"name":"56:57","price":"It is We Who created you; why do you not then believe [in resurrection]?","arabic":"نَحۡنُ خَلَقۡنَٰكُمۡ فَلَوۡلَا تُصَدِّقُونَ","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":5036,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"en"},{"name":"56:58","price":"Have you thought about the semen that you emit?","arabic":"أَفَرَءَيۡتُم مَّا تُمۡنُونَ","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":5037,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"en"},{"name":"56:59","price":"Is it you who create it, or is it We Who are the Creators?","arabic":"ءَأَنتُمۡ تَخۡلُقُونَهُۥٓ أَمۡ نَحۡنُ ٱلۡخَٰلِقُونَ","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":5038,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"en"},{"name":"56:60","price":"We have ordained death among you, and nothing can overcome us","arabic":"نَحۡنُ قَدَّرۡنَا بَيۡنَكُمُ ٱلۡمَوۡتَ وَمَا نَحۡنُ بِمَسۡبُوقِينَ","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":5039,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"en"},{"name":"56:61","price":"from transforming you and recreating you in forms that you do not know[7].","arabic":"عَلَىٰٓ أَن نُّبَدِّلَ أَمۡثَٰلَكُمۡ وَنُنشِئَكُمۡ فِي مَا لَا تَعۡلَمُونَ","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":5040,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"[7] Or \"from replacing you by others like yourselves [in this life] and creating you [in the Hereafter] in that which you do not know.\"","lang":"en"},{"name":"56:62","price":"You are well aware of the first creation; why do you not then take heed?","arabic":"وَلَقَدۡ عَلِمۡتُمُ ٱلنَّشۡأَةَ ٱلۡأُولَىٰ فَلَوۡلَا تَذَكَّرُونَ","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":5041,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"en"},{"name":"56:63","price":"Have you thought about what you sow?","arabic":"أَفَرَءَيۡتُم مَّا تَحۡرُثُونَ","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":5042,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"en"},{"name":"56:64","price":"Is it you who cause it to grow, or is it We Who make it grow?","arabic":"ءَأَنتُمۡ تَزۡرَعُونَهُۥٓ أَمۡ نَحۡنُ ٱلزَّٰرِعُونَ","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":5043,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"en"},{"name":"56:65","price":"If We willed, We could reduce your harvest to rubble, leaving you to wonder and lament,","arabic":"لَوۡ نَشَآءُ لَجَعَلۡنَٰهُ حُطَٰمٗا فَظَلۡتُمۡ تَفَكَّهُونَ","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":5044,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"en"},{"name":"56:66","price":"“We suffered loss,","arabic":"إِنَّا لَمُغۡرَمُونَ","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":5045,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"en"},{"name":"56:67","price":"rather, we are deprived.”","arabic":"بَلۡ نَحۡنُ مَحۡرُومُونَ","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":5046,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"en"},{"name":"56:68","price":"Have you thought about the water that you drink?","arabic":"أَفَرَءَيۡتُمُ ٱلۡمَآءَ ٱلَّذِي تَشۡرَبُونَ","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":5047,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"en"},{"name":"56:69","price":"Is it you who bring it down from the clouds, or is it We Who bring it down?","arabic":"ءَأَنتُمۡ أَنزَلۡتُمُوهُ مِنَ ٱلۡمُزۡنِ أَمۡ نَحۡنُ ٱلۡمُنزِلُونَ","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":5048,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"en"},{"name":"56:70","price":"If We willed, We could make it salty; will you not then give thanks?","arabic":"لَوۡ نَشَآءُ جَعَلۡنَٰهُ أُجَاجٗا فَلَوۡلَا تَشۡكُرُونَ","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":5049,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"en"},{"name":"56:71","price":"Have you thought about the fire that you kindle?","arabic":"أَفَرَءَيۡتُمُ ٱلنَّارَ ٱلَّتِي تُورُونَ","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":5050,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"en"},{"name":"56:72","price":"Is it you who produced its trees[8], or is it We Who produced it?","arabic":"ءَأَنتُمۡ أَنشَأۡتُمۡ شَجَرَتَهَآ أَمۡ نَحۡنُ ٱلۡمُنشِـُٔونَ","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":5051,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"[8] Referring to Arabian trees, markh and ‘afār, which produce fire when their green branches are rubbed against each other.","lang":"en"},{"name":"56:73","price":"We made it a reminder [of the Hellfire] and a benefit for the travelers[9].","arabic":"نَحۡنُ جَعَلۡنَٰهَا تَذۡكِرَةٗ وَمَتَٰعٗا لِّلۡمُقۡوِينَ","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":5052,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"[9] By which they ignite fire. Travelers are mentioned in particular because it is of special convenience to them, although it is of use for all people in general.","lang":"en"},{"name":"56:74","price":"So glorify the Name of your Lord, the Most Great.","arabic":"فَسَبِّحۡ بِٱسۡمِ رَبِّكَ ٱلۡعَظِيمِ","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":5053,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"en"},{"name":"56:75","price":"I do swear[10] by the positions of the stars –","arabic":"۞ فَلَآ أُقۡسِمُ بِمَوَٰقِعِ ٱلنُّجُومِ","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":5054,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"[10] The negative article \"la\" (nay) means: The truth is not what is said or thought by disbelievers or others. The oath refutes certain objections of the disbelievers with regard to the Qur’an.","lang":"en"},{"name":"56:76","price":"and this is indeed a great oath, if only you knew –","arabic":"وَإِنَّهُۥ لَقَسَمٞ لَّوۡ تَعۡلَمُونَ عَظِيمٌ","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":5055,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"en"},{"name":"56:77","price":"that this is indeed a noble Qur’an,","arabic":"إِنَّهُۥ لَقُرۡءَانٞ كَرِيمٞ","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":5056,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"en"},{"name":"56:78","price":"in a well-preserved Record[11],","arabic":"فِي كِتَٰبٖ مَّكۡنُونٖ","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":5057,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"[11] i.e., the Preserved Tablet.","lang":"en"},{"name":"56:79","price":"that none can touch except the purified ones[12] –","arabic":"لَّا يَمَسُّهُۥٓ إِلَّا ٱلۡمُطَهَّرُونَ","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":5058,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"[12] i.e., angels. It refutes the claim of the pagans that the Qur’an was sent down by devils. (See 26:210-212). Based on this verse, many Muslim jurists held that one should perform ablution prior to reading the Qur’an.","lang":"en"},{"name":"56:80","price":"a revelation from the Lord of the worlds.","arabic":"تَنزِيلٞ مِّن رَّبِّ ٱلۡعَٰلَمِينَ","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":5059,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"en"},{"name":"56:81","price":"Do you take this discourse lightly,","arabic":"أَفَبِهَٰذَا ٱلۡحَدِيثِ أَنتُم مُّدۡهِنُونَ","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":5060,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"en"},{"name":"56:82","price":"and instead [of thanking Allah] for the provision you are given, you show ingratitude?","arabic":"وَتَجۡعَلُونَ رِزۡقَكُمۡ أَنَّكُمۡ تُكَذِّبُونَ","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":5061,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"en"},{"name":"56:83","price":"Then why [are you helpless] when the soul reaches the throat,","arabic":"فَلَوۡلَآ إِذَا بَلَغَتِ ٱلۡحُلۡقُومَ","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":5062,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"en"},{"name":"56:84","price":"while you are looking on,","arabic":"وَأَنتُمۡ حِينَئِذٖ تَنظُرُونَ","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":5063,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"en"},{"name":"56:85","price":"when We are closer[13] to him than you, but you do not see?","arabic":"وَنَحۡنُ أَقۡرَبُ إِلَيۡهِ مِنكُمۡ وَلَٰكِن لَّا تُبۡصِرُونَ","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":5064,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"[13] We are closer to him in terms of Knowledge and Power; Our angels are closer in person.","lang":"en"},{"name":"56:86","price":"If you are not subject to retribution, then why do you not","arabic":"فَلَوۡلَآ إِن كُنتُمۡ غَيۡرَ مَدِينِينَ","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":5065,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"en"},{"name":"56:87","price":"bring that [soul] back, if you are truthful?","arabic":"تَرۡجِعُونَهَآ إِن كُنتُمۡ صَٰدِقِينَ","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":5066,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"en"},{"name":"56:88","price":"If that dying person is one of those who will be brought near to Allah,","arabic":"فَأَمَّآ إِن كَانَ مِنَ ٱلۡمُقَرَّبِينَ","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":5067,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"en"},{"name":"56:89","price":"then [he will have] comfort, fragrance[14], and a Garden of Bliss.","arabic":"فَرَوۡحٞ وَرَيۡحَانٞ وَجَنَّتُ نَعِيمٖ","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":5068,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"[14] lit., fragrant basil. Paradise is described in the Qur’an as being pleasant to the eye, the heart, and the ear. Here it also emphasizes the scent.","lang":"en"},{"name":"56:90","price":"If he is one of the people of the right,","arabic":"وَأَمَّآ إِن كَانَ مِنۡ أَصۡحَٰبِ ٱلۡيَمِينِ","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":5069,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"en"},{"name":"56:91","price":"[He will be told], “Peace be to you, for being one of the people of the right.”","arabic":"فَسَلَٰمٞ لَّكَ مِنۡ أَصۡحَٰبِ ٱلۡيَمِينِ","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":5070,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"en"},{"name":"56:92","price":"But if he is one of the misguided deniers,","arabic":"وَأَمَّآ إِن كَانَ مِنَ ٱلۡمُكَذِّبِينَ ٱلضَّآلِّينَ","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":5071,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"en"},{"name":"56:93","price":"then he will be welcomed with scalding water,","arabic":"فَنُزُلٞ مِّنۡ حَمِيمٖ","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":5072,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"en"},{"name":"56:94","price":"and he will burn in Blazing Fire.","arabic":"وَتَصۡلِيَةُ جَحِيمٍ","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":5073,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"en"},{"name":"56:95","price":"This is indeed the absolute truth.","arabic":"إِنَّ هَٰذَا لَهُوَ حَقُّ ٱلۡيَقِينِ","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":5074,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"en"},{"name":"56:96","price":"So glorify the name of your Lord, the Most Great.","arabic":"فَسَبِّحۡ بِٱسۡمِ رَبِّكَ ٱلۡعَظِيمِ","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":5075,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"en"}],"chapter":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah","Chapter Al-Waqi'ah","Waqi'ah","Surah Waqi'ah","Chapter Waqi'ah","Al Waqi'ah","Surah Al Waqi'ah","Chapter Al Waqi'ah","Surah 56","Chapter 56","The Inevitable","الواقعة"]}